For more details, refer to Troubleshooting.
.SH VERSION
.PP
v3.4.14/v5.8.4 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Count the number of lobs in the collection "sample.lob", without specifying the
parameter "cond".
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
db.sample.lob.lobCount()
\f[]
.fi
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
Count the number of LOBs that meet the conditions and have a size greater than
1MB.
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.sample.lob.lobCount({Size: {$gt:1024*1024*1024}})
\f[]
.fi
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
Count the number of LOB pieces that meet the condition where Oid is
"000067c20f5232000457d32a".
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.sample.lob.lobCount().hint({Oid:"000067c20f5232000457d32a",ListPieces:true})
\f[]
.fi
.RE
